---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Actors Theatre Rajasthan" 
  description="Privacy Policy for Actors Theatre Rajasthan (ATR)."
>
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="page-container">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-content">
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> January 1, 2024</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>At Actors Theatre Rajasthan (ATR), we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, and mailing address when you voluntarily provide it to us through our website, workshop registrations, ticket bookings, or donation forms.</p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Process registrations for workshops, academies, and events.</li>
          <li>Communicate with you regarding our upcoming productions, festivals, and activities.</li>
          <li>Process donations and issue applicable tax receipts.</li>
          <li>Respond to inquiries, collaborations, or feedback.</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Protection and Sharing</h2>
        <p>We are committed to protecting your personal information. We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal identification information to third parties. We may share generic aggregated demographic information not linked to any personal identification information regarding visitors and users with our trusted partners for the purposes outlined above.</p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to external sites that are not operated by us. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that third party's site. We strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of every site you visit. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services.</p>

        <h2>5. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>ATR reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. We encourage users to frequently check this page for any changes. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this privacy policy periodically and become aware of modifications.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices of this site, or your dealings with this site, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@actorstheatrerajasthan.org</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> P-3 Kisan Marg, W-2, Madhuban Colony, Tonk Road, Jaipur – 302015, Rajasthan</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    padding-top: var(--nav-height);
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 400px);
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  .policy-content {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .policy-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .policy-content ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .policy-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
